.TH "set_con2fb_map" 9 "set_con2fb_map" "May 2021" "Kernel Hacker's Manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
set_con2fb_map \- map console to frame buffer device
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "int" set_con2fb_map
.BI "(int unit "  ","
.BI "int newidx "  ","
.BI "int user "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "unit" 12
virtual console number to map
.IP "newidx" 12
frame buffer index to map virtual console to
.IP "user" 12
user request

Maps a virtual console \fIunit\fP to a frame buffer device
\fInewidx\fP.

This should be called with the console lock held.
